data.!description: Binding information for chart - if not specified it is created from the metadata information

idPrefix.!description: Prefix added to the generated ID of the value help

presentation.!description: Metadata path to the presentation (UI.Chart w or w/o qualifier)

useFormContainerLabels.!description: Control the rendering of the form container labels

entitySet.!description: Metadata path to the entity set

createMode.!description: Control the create mode of the form

_valueList.!description: Temporary workaround only path to valuelist

displayHeader.!description: Flag to check whether the Contact is present in Display header or not

collection.!description: Metadata path to the entitySet or navigationProperty

editMode.!description: Control the edit mode of the form

chartType.!description: The chart type (Column, Bar, etc.) - if not specified chartType is picked from the metadata information

conditionModel.!description: Indicator whether the field help is for a filter field

header.!description: The header text of the chart - if not specified it is picked up from the metadata information

sap.fe.macros.Form.!description:
Macro for creating a Form based on provided OData v4 metadata. Usage example: 
<macro:Form
 id="SomeID"
 entitySet="{entitySet>}"
 facet="{facet>}"
 formTitle="someTitle"
 editMode="Editable"
 createMode="true"
 useFormContainerLabels="true"
 partOfPreview="true"
 onChange=".handlers.onFieldValueChange"
/>
